		}
		{
			description: [
				"While fishing near the coast, your line catches something unexpected — not a fish, but a waterlogged bottle."
				""
				"Inside, a salt-stained note reads:"
				""
				"&o&9\"If you find this, the &nHarbinger&r&o&9 has already sunk. Follow the twin lanterns east. The chest is still aboard. Do not let &4Salazar&r find it first.\"&r&r"
				""
				"&o&8You look up. Through the fog, two faint glowing shapes bob in the distance...&r&r"
			]
			icon: "aquaculture:message_in_a_bottle"
			id: "60A1F473F0238E74"
			rewards: [{
				id: "29A37DC14CE8EF43"
				type: "xp"
				xp: 20
			}]
			tasks: [
				{
					biome: "minecraft:beach"
					id: "43A51C79B8CC2907"
					title: "Stand on a beach shore"
					type: "biome"
				}
				{
					consume_items: true
					id: "556DAA496239C8C0"
					item: "aquaculture:message_in_a_bottle"
					type: "item"
				}
			]
			title: "Message in a Bottle"
			x: 30.0d
			y: -13.5d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["60A1F473F0238E74"]
			description: [
				"You follow the glowing lanterns and wade into the shallows."
				""
				"&9The wreck of the Harbinger&r lies half-buried in the sand, her hull split open by time and storm. Seaweed clings to the broken masts like mourning veils."
				""
				"&o&8You've heard of this ship. Traders spoke of her captain — a privateer who turned pirate after being betrayed by the merchant guild. They say he went down with something valuable. Something people have been searching for ever since.&r&r"
				""
				"The ruins are not empty."
			]
			hide_until_deps_complete: true
			hide_until_deps_visible: true
			icon: "minecraft:nautilus_shell"
			id: "2A5FDC53A9A4B337"
			rewards: [{
				id: "3500692B7B5873FF"
				type: "xp"
				xp: 30
			}]
			tasks: [
				{
					id: "1E7EA6E7BA06767F"
					structure: "minecraft:shipwreck"
					type: "structure"
				}
				{
					count: 5L
					id: "05E0640C8450C488"
					item: "minecraft:nautilus_shell"
					type: "item"
				}
			]
			title: "The Wreck of the Harbinger"
			x: 31.5d
			y: -13.5d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["2A5FDC53A9A4B337"]
			description: [
				"Below the waterline, half-buried in silt and barnacles, you find the captain's quarters."
				""
				"There is no treasure chest. But there is a name carved into the wall with a knife:"
				""
				"&4&o\"SALAZAR — OCEAN MONUMENT — EAST\"&r&r"
				""
				"&o&8So &4Salazar&r got here first. He found the location and left this as a taunt. Or a warning. Either way, he's heading to the Ocean Monument, and whatever the captain hid is there waiting.&r&r"
				""
				"You'll need to prepare. The monument is deep, cold, and guarded by things that don't take kindly to visitors."
			]
			hide_until_deps_complete: true
			hide_until_deps_visible: true
			icon: "minecraft:paper"
			id: "786812927C83EC71"
			rewards: [{
				id: "12E3807B29E6A4C8"
				item: {
					Count: 1
					id: "supplementaries:cartographers_quill"
					tag: {
						display: {
							Name: "{\"text\":\"Salazar's scratched note\"}"
						}
						maxSearchRadius: 300
						skipKnown: 1b
						targetStructure: "minecraft:ocean_monument"
						zoomLevel: 2
					}
				}
				type: "item"
			}]
			tasks: [
				{
					consume_items: true
					id: "4A81D46A29532CFC"
					item: {
						Count: 1
						id: "minecraft:potion"
						tag: {
							Potion: "minecraft:water_breathing"
						}
					}
					type: "item"
				}
				{
					id: "09F74C192643AE41"
					item: {
						Count: 1
						id: "minecraft:iron_helmet"
						tag: {
							Damage: 0
							Enchantments: [{
								id: "minecraft:aqua_affinity"
								lvl: 1s
							}]
						}
					}
					type: "item"
				}
			]
			title: "Prepare for the Deep"
			x: 33.0d
			y: -13.5d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["786812927C83EC71"]
			description: [
				"&9The Ocean Monument&r looms from the dark water like a forgotten cathedral."
				""
				"Its stone corridors are patrolled by Guardians — ancient constructs that seem almost... deliberate. As if placed here to protect something specific."
				""
				"&o&8You push deeper, past the Elder Guardian's territory, into the monument's flooded heart. And there — wedged between two prismarine pillars — is a chest bearing the privateer's emblem. A compass rose, surrounded by a serpent biting its own tail.&r&r"
				""
				"The chest is sealed with an unusual lock."
				""
				"&4Salazar hasn't opened it yet. You arrived in time."
			]
			hide_until_deps_complete: true
			hide_until_deps_visible: true
			icon: {
				Count: 1
				id: "ftbquests:custom_icon"
				tag: {
					Icon: "minecraft:textures/block/prismarine.png"
				}
			}
			id: "0A2B64BF18182507"
			rewards: [
				{
					id: "5BC67595E6276E82"
					type: "xp"
					xp: 50
				}
				{
					count: 8
					id: "39ADC9DE5E02F949"
					item: "minecraft:prismarine_crystals"
					type: "item"
				}
			]
			tasks: [
				{
					id: "41A822752CBBF2EB"
					structure: "minecraft:ocean_monument"
					type: "structure"
				}
				{
					entity: "minecraft:elder_guardian"
