		{
			dependencies: ["43786F9835A6F8C5"]
			description: [
				"The forest grows darker as you press deeper."
				""
				"The trees here are wrong — their bark is black and slick, their leaves a sickly violet. The ground beneath your feet is soft and warm, as if something breathes below it."
				""
				"&4&oThe corrupted spirit is close.&r&r"
				""
				"&o&8Maren warned you about this place. The corruption spreads outward from the spirit's resting point — a grove where no birds sing and no animals walk. You must confront it before it grows strong enough to leave the forest entirely.&r&r"
			]
