		}
		{
			dependencies: ["383426FBF6B0B4D3"]
			description: [
				"Inside the Desert Temple, beneath the false floor and past the TNT trap, you find an antechamber that doesn't appear on any map."
				""
				"The walls are lined with amber panels, and at the room's centre sits a stone plinth where something once rested — recently removed."
				""
				"&6&o\"THE THRONE WAS HERE.\"&r&r"
				""
				"&o&8The tablet in your pack vibrates. You pull it out and the glyphs are glowing faintly. Someone moved the Amber Throne recently — and whatever seal kept it dormant left with it.&r&r"
				""
				"A second inscription on the plinth, in the common tongue — scratched hurriedly by someone after the ancient builders:"
				""
				"&4&o\"Do not seek the Throne. Do not approach the Throne. Bury this again.\"&r&r"
				""
				"Too late for that."
			]
			hide_until_deps_complete: true
			hide_until_deps_visible: true
			icon: "minecraft:chiseled_sandstone"
			id: "3F0CA1B27BA42F27"
			rewards: [{
				id: "0B5028A64DB77918"
				type: "xp"
				xp: 40
			}]
			tasks: [{
				id: "6C2BD7FABD2954B6"
				structure: "minecraft:desert_pyramid"
				type: "structure"
			}]
			title: "Inside the Temple"
			x: 33.0d
			y: -6.0d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["3F0CA1B27BA42F27"]
			description: [
				"Tracking the Throne leads you to a second, larger ruin — a half-collapsed palace, its entrance flanked by two enormous amber-eyed statues."
				""
				"&6The Amber Palace.&r"
				""
				"&o&8The statues' eyes follow you as you approach. Not a trick of the light. They are watching. Something inside this place is already aware of your presence.&r&r"
				""
				"The air inside the palace is thick and dry, tasting of ozone and old stone. Every footstep echoes like a drumbeat."
				""
				"The Throne room lies ahead — and the tablet in your pack is burning now."
			]
			hide_until_deps_complete: true
			hide_until_deps_visible: true
			icon: {
				Count: 1
